OpenBlockPlugin - Class in org.block.plugin.standard
This is the class which if a object requires a plugin but comes as default will be used This is not used within the loading pool, like other plugins and cannot be disabled While its not in the loading pool, you can use it as a dependent, mainly for version checking This is also not provided within the Blocks.getPlugins() or Blocks.getEnabledPlugins() launchFrom is disabled as this is not launched, it is just context
